+This strategy starts at the canonicity gate, not at a packet-level sign computation. The predecessor exact-NS line already established that packetization without a fixed support convention, projection rule, leakage instantiation, and restored exact-network rule is not one theorem-facing object. The only genuinely new ingredient for this mission is the singleton sign clue plus the proposed split into `SD_part` and `SD_target`.
